<p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>We are pleased to inform you that your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>", has been successfully created on Gighive.</p>

<h3>Task Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %></li>
  <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @task.status.capitalize %></li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Thank you for choosing Gighive!</p>
